S

schedule() - Method in class elfarol.ElFarolContextBuilder
Main schedule of the simulation containing the following phases: First, all agents determine if their attend to the bar based on their knowledge (strategies) and the prediction Then we update the global history At the end of the turn when the new attendance level is known, all of the agents update their best strategy
score(AStrategy) - Method in class elfarol.AgentWeighted
Evaluates the fitness value of the specified strategy based on the current knowledge of the agent (i.e., based on the current state recorded in the memory of the agent).
strategies - Variable in class elfarol.AgentWeighted
